SELECT 
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_client_ods.client_display_name,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_client_ods.client_type,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS CLIENT_TYPE,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(CAST('V4' AS CHAR),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS SOURCE_SYSTEM,
	CAST(SRC_client_ods.medicare  AS SIGNED) AS V_MEDICARE,
	CAST(SRC_client_ods.medicaid  AS SIGNED) AS V_MEDICAID,
	CAST(SRC_client_ods.commercial  AS SIGNED) AS V_COMMERCIAL,
	CAST(SRC_client_ods.national_accounts  AS SIGNED) AS V_NATIONAL_ACCOUNTS,
	CAST(SRC_client_ods.is_deleted  AS SIGNED) AS V_IS_DELETED,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(RTRIM(LTRIM(CAST(SRC_client_ods.parent_pid  AS CHAR)))
,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS V_PARENT_PID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(SRC_client_ods.client_pid  AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS V_SUB_CLIENT_PID
 FROM $DO_GHL1_MY_BOLD_ODS_CLIENT_ODS SRC_client_ods 

WHERE 
SRC_client_ods.client_pid  IS NOT NULL 
AND SRC_client_ods.parent_pid IS NOT NULL
AND SRC_client_ods.is_current = 1

WITH SRC_dim_client  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_client.client_key AS CLIENT_KEY
	,SRC_dim_client.client_pid AS CLIENT_PID
 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_CLIENT SRC_dim_client  
 WHERE 
	SRC_dim_client.source_system = 'V4' 
) 
,  JNR_NAME 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_client_ods.CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME AS CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME
	,SRC_client_ods.CLIENT_TYPE AS CLIENT_TYPE
	,SRC_client_ods.SOURCE_SYSTEM AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,SRC_client_ods.V_MEDICARE AS V_MEDICARE
	,SRC_client_ods.V_MEDICAID AS V_MEDICAID
	,SRC_client_ods.V_COMMERCIAL AS V_COMMERCIAL
	,SRC_client_ods.V_NATIONAL_ACCOUNTS AS V_NATIONAL_ACCOUNTS
	,SRC_client_ods.V_IS_DELETED AS V_IS_DELETED
	,SRC_client_ods.V_SUB_CLIENT_PID AS V_SUB_CLIENT_PID
	,SRC_dim_client.CLIENT_KEY AS CLIENT_KEY
  FROM 
	$TFORM_SRC_client_ods SRC_client_ods 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_dim_client 
ON
(SRC_client_ods.V_PARENT_PID  = SRC_dim_client.CLIENT_PID ) 
) 
,  EXPR_NAME 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	JNR_NAME.CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME AS CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME
	,JNR_NAME.CLIENT_TYPE AS CLIENT_TYPE
	,JNR_NAME.SOURCE_SYSTEM AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,JNR_NAME.V_MEDICARE AS V_MEDICARE
	,JNR_NAME.V_MEDICAID AS V_MEDICAID
	,JNR_NAME.V_COMMERCIAL AS V_COMMERCIAL
	,JNR_NAME.V_NATIONAL_ACCOUNTS AS V_NATIONAL_ACCOUNTS
	,JNR_NAME.V_IS_DELETED AS V_IS_DELETED
	,JNR_NAME.V_SUB_CLIENT_PID AS V_SUB_CLIENT_PID
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TS
	,CASE WHEN JNR_NAME.CLIENT_KEY  IS NULL THEN -1 ELSE JNR_NAME.CLIENT_KEY END AS CLIENT_KEY
	,($SP_MAX_KEY.max_key  + row_number() OVER (ORDER BY (select 1))) AS SUB_CLIENT_KEY
 FROM 
	JNR_NAME
)MERGE $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_SUB_CLIENT TGT_dim_sub_client 
 USING EXPR_NAME EXPR_NAME 
  ON TGT_dim_sub_client.source_system = EXPR_NAME.SOURCE_SYSTEM AND 
TGT_dim_sub_client.sub_client_pid = EXPR_NAME.V_SUB_CLIENT_PID
 WHEN MATCHED THEN 
UPDATE SET
	sub_client_type = EXPR_NAME.CLIENT_TYPE
	,sub_client_name = EXPR_NAME.CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME
	,commercial = EXPR_NAME.V_COMMERCIAL
	,medicare = EXPR_NAME.V_MEDICARE
	,medicaid = EXPR_NAME.V_MEDICAID
	,national_accounts = EXPR_NAME.V_NATIONAL_ACCOUNTS
	,updated_at = EXPR_NAME.CURRENT_TS
	,is_deleted = EXPR_NAME.V_IS_DELETED
 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
INSERT
(sub_client_key,sub_client_pid,sub_client_type,sub_client_name,client_key,commercial,medicare,medicaid,national_accounts,source_system,created_at,updated_at,is_deleted)
VALUES (
EXPR_NAME.SUB_CLIENT_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.V_SUB_CLIENT_PID,
EXPR_NAME.CLIENT_TYPE,
EXPR_NAME.CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME,
EXPR_NAME.CLIENT_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.V_COMMERCIAL,
EXPR_NAME.V_MEDICARE,
EXPR_NAME.V_MEDICAID,
EXPR_NAME.V_NATIONAL_ACCOUNTS,
EXPR_NAME.SOURCE_SYSTEM,
EXPR_NAME.CURRENT_TS,
EXPR_NAME.CURRENT_TS,
EXPR_NAME.V_IS_DELETED)#SEMICOLON_DELIM#

	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_client_campaign_ods.operations_mgr,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS OPERATIONS_MGR,
	coalesce(DATE_FORMAT(SRC_client_campaign_ods.expected_kit_ship_date,'%Y-%m-%d'),'') AS EXPECTED_KIT_SHIP_DATE,
	coalesce(DATE_FORMAT(SRC_client_campaign_ods.launch_date,'%Y-%m-%d'),'') AS LAUNCH_DATE,
	coalesce(DATE_FORMAT(SRC_client_campaign_ods.completion_date,'%Y-%m-%d'),'') AS COMPLETION_DATE,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_client_campaign_ods.status,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS STATUS,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_client_campaign_ods.program_project_sfid,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS PROGRAM_PROJECT_SFID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(CAST('V4' AS CHAR),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS SOURCE_SYSTEM,
	CAST(SRC_client_campaign_ods.lab_claim_billing   AS SIGNED) AS V_LAB_CLAIM_BILLING,
	CAST(SRC_client_campaign_ods.keep_open  AS SIGNED) AS V_KEEP_OPEN,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(SRC_client_campaign_ods.client_pid  AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_SUB_CLIENT_PID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(SRC_client_campaign_ods.client_campaign_pid  AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_CAMPAIGN_PID
 FROM $DO_GHL1_MY_BOLD_ODS_CLIENT_CAMPAIGN_ODS SRC_client_campaign_ods 

WHERE  SRC_client_campaign_ods.client_campaign_pid IS NOT NULL
AND SRC_client_campaign_ods.is_current  = 1

WITH  JNR_NAME 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_client_campaign_ods.CAMPAIGN AS CAMPAIGN
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.CAMPAIGN_DESC AS CAMPAIGN_DESC
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.CLIENT_MGR AS CLIENT_MGR
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.IMPL_MGR AS IMPL_MGR
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.OPERATIONS_MGR AS OPERATIONS_MGR
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.EXPECTED_KIT_SHIP_DATE AS EXPECTED_KIT_SHIP_DATE
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.LAUNCH_DATE AS LAUNCH_DATE
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.COMPLETION_DATE AS COMPLETION_DATE
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.STATUS AS STATUS
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.PROGRAM_PROJECT_SFID AS PROGRAM_PROJECT_SFID
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.SOURCE_SYSTEM AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.V_LAB_CLAIM_BILLING AS V_LAB_CLAIM_BILLING
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.V_KEEP_OPEN AS V_KEEP_OPEN
	,SRC_client_campaign_ods.V_CAMPAIGN_PID AS V_CAMPAIGN_PID
	,SRC_dim_sub_client.SUB_CLIENT_KEY AS SUB_CLIENT_KEY
  FROM 
	$TFORM_SRC_client_campaign_ods SRC_client_campaign_ods 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_SUB_CLIENT SRC_dim_sub_client 
ON
(SRC_client_campaign_ods.V_SUB_CLIENT_PID  = SRC_dim_sub_client.SUB_CLIENT_PID AND
SRC_client_campaign_ods.SOURCE_SYSTEM = SRC_dim_sub_client.SOURCE_SYSTEM ) 
) 
,  EXPR_NAME 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	JNR_NAME.CAMPAIGN AS CAMPAIGN
	,JNR_NAME.CAMPAIGN_DESC AS CAMPAIGN_DESC
	,JNR_NAME.CLIENT_MGR AS CLIENT_MGR
	,JNR_NAME.IMPL_MGR AS IMPL_MGR
	,JNR_NAME.OPERATIONS_MGR AS OPERATIONS_MGR
	,JNR_NAME.EXPECTED_KIT_SHIP_DATE AS EXPECTED_KIT_SHIP_DATE

	,0 AS IS_DELETED
	,CASE WHEN JNR_NAME.SUB_CLIENT_KEY  IS NULL THEN -1 ELSE JNR_NAME.SUB_CLIENT_KEY  END AS V_SUB_CLIENT_KEY
	,($SP_MAX_KEY.max_key  + row_number() OVER (ORDER BY (select 1))) AS CAMPAIGN_KEY
 FROM 
	JNR_NAME
)MERGE $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_CAMPAIGN TGT_dim_campaign 
 USING EXPR_NAME EXPR_NAME 
  ON TGT_dim_campaign.source_system = EXPR_NAME.SOURCE_SYSTEM AND
